{"title":"Columbus Trittico Components","link":"https://theradavist.com/columbus-trittico-components/","date":1720789224000,"content":"<p><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/Victoire-500-22.jpeg?fit=1200,1333&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/Victoire-500-22.jpeg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/Victoire-500-22.jpeg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/Victoire-500-22.jpeg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/Victoire-500-22.jpeg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p><em>The <a href=\"https://www.columbus1919.com/trittico\" target=\"_blank\">Columbus Trittico</a> line includes handlebars, stems, seatposts, forks, and bottle cages. These components are designed blend seamlessly with a variety of frame materials. Let’s check them out.</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img width=\"2880\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/trittico_components-stem.jpg?fit=1200,1920&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/trittico_components-stem.jpg?w=2880&amp;quality=75 2880w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/trittico_components-stem.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/trittico_components-stem.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/trittico_components-stem.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/trittico_components-stem.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/trittico_components-stem.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Trittico Stem</strong></p>\n<p>With a refined Italian minimalist design and a proprietary micro-tuning fit system, the Trittico Stem is ideal for a newly handmade frame or an exclusive upgrade to an existing cockpit system. Features include the Tuning Sleeve for precise fit adjustments, allowing for 5º angle adjustment and 5 mm reach adjustment, hidden bolts for a clean aesthetic, and a lightweight, cold-forged aluminum front plate for optimal handlebar connection.</p>\n<p><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/trittico_components-fork_3x.0f8d.jpg?fit=1200,1333&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/trittico_components-fork_3x.0f8d.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/trittico_components-fork_3x.0f8d.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/trittico_components-fork_3x.0f8d.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/trittico_components-fork_3x.0f8d.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Trittico Road Integrated Fork</strong></p>\n<p>The patent-pending trefoil steerer section of the Futura fork allows for integrated cable routing in a 1-1/8” headset favored by leading frame builders. This innovation offers an optimal balance of rigidity and performance, with a magnetic smart brake mount cover to maintain a minimalist aesthetic.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/trittico_components-handlebar_3xa.jpg?fit=1200,1333&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/trittico_components-handlebar_3xa.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/trittico_components-handlebar_3xa.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/trittico_components-handlebar_3xa.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/trittico_components-handlebar_3xa.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Trittico Road Handlebar</strong></p>\n<p>Designed for contemporary road racing, this ergonomic carbon fiber handlebar offers market-leading performance, integrated cable routing, and race-specific ergonomics. Features include a crescent-shaped incision for improved fit and an ergonomic lower half for secure grip during sprints.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/trittico_components-seatpost_3x.jpg?fit=1200,1333&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/trittico_components-seatpost_3x.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/trittico_components-seatpost_3x.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/trittico_components-seatpost_3x.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/trittico_components-seatpost_3x.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Trittico Seatpost</strong></p>\n<p>Featuring a patent-pending micro-adjustment system, the Trittico seatpost combines high performance with ease of use. It includes an Intuitive Tuning System for precise saddle adjustments, dual offset options, and a modular design for easy maintenance.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/trittico_components-bottlecage_3.jpg?fit=1200,1333&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/trittico_components-bottlecage_3.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/trittico_components-bottlecage_3.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/trittico_components-bottlecage_3.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/trittico_components-bottlecage_3.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/trittico_components-race-spoo.jpg?fit=1200,1333&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/trittico_components-race-spoo.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/trittico_components-race-spoo.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/trittico_components-race-spoo.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/trittico_components-race-spoo.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Trittico Bottle Cage and Race Spoon GPS Mount</strong></p>\n<p>Hyper-minimal designer accessories to complete your Trittico kit, made from carbon fiber, Titanium hardware and CNC’d 6061 T6 aluminium.</p>\n<p>Here is a selection of bikes featuring the Trittico components…</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/Trittico-Onguza-credit-%40huffy808foto-%40dylanvanweelden-2.jpg?fit=1200,1334&amp;quality=75\" /><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/Trittico-Onguza-credit-%40huffy808foto-%40dylanvanweelden-1.jpg?fit=1200,1334&amp;quality=75\" /><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/Trittico-Onguza-credit-%40huffy808foto-%40dylanvanweelden-4.jpg?fit=1200,1334&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><em>Photos credit <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/huffy808foto/\" target=\"_blank\">@huffy808foto</a> <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/dylanvanweelden/?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\">@dylanvanweelden</a></em></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/01_before_assembly_Fork_2023_MADE_071.jpg?fit=1200,1333&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/01_before_assembly_Fork_2023_MADE_071.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/01_before_assembly_Fork_2023_MADE_071.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/01_before_assembly_Fork_2023_MADE_071.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/01_before_assembly_Fork_2023_MADE_071.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p><em>Photo credit <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/ioklin_frameworks/\" target=\"_blank\">@Lok_Lin</a></em></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/Victoire-500-2.jpeg?fit=1200,1334&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/Victoire-500-2.jpeg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/Victoire-500-2.jpeg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/Victoire-500-2.jpeg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/Victoire-500-2.jpeg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p><em>Photo via <a href=\"https://www.victoire-cycles.com/en/\" target=\"_blank\">Victoire Cycles</a></em></p>\n<p>Check out more information, including lots of neat product videos at <a href=\"https://www.columbus1919.com/trittico\" target=\"_blank\">Columbus</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/columbus-trittico-components/\">Columbus Trittico Components</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"baab639c3ed538cf8c45488b89ea0240d8fa0d37c4ad48abb5e88d33a5d875cc","category":"Cycling"}